          <strong>1. Pin Capture to get the most out of it</strong> <span>💪🏼</span> 
        </h2>       
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <%= cl_image_tag "v1626465177/Screen_Shot_2021-07-16_at_9.52.50_PM_oyjwuq.png", class: "how-to-2" %>  
        <h2 class="about-us-subtitle-text">
          <strong>2. Highlight and press the Capture  button to save and share your snippet </strong> <span>🌍</span> 
        </h2>       
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <%= cl_image_tag "v1626465268/Screen_Shot_2021-07-16_at_9.54.22_PM_jcoxlg.png", class: "how-to-3" %>  
