          <strong>4. Disable or turn capture off  by clicking the Capture logo </strong> <span>🌗</span> 
        </h2>       
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <%= cl_image_tag "v1627581212/Screen_Shot_2021-07-29_at_7.50.45_PM_yzrvcb.png", class: "how-to-5" %>   
