          <strong>5. Enter private mode under your profile section <span>🕵🏻‍♂️</span></strong> 
        </h2>       
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box">
      <h2 class="about-us-subtitle-text">
        <strong id="done-text"><span>🏁</span> You're all set to go <span>🏎</span></strong> 
